      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 23:26:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国数据强劲，债券暴跌，股市涨跌互现：市场休整</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲市场开盘涨跌不一，美国股市小幅走低，美国国债大量抛售，因为美国工厂数据强劲，加剧了人们对美联储不会急于降息的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 21:58:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国希望没收与前刚果领导人有关的纽约豪华公寓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/us-seeks-forfeiture-of-luxury-apartment-in-trump-hotel-and-tower</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据周一在纽约公开的法庭文件显示，美国正试图没收曼哈顿的一套豪华公寓，据称该公寓是用从刚果政府掠夺的资金为该国长期总统丹尼斯·萨苏·恩格索的女儿购买的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/us-seeks-forfeiture-of-luxury-apartment-in-trump-hotel-and-tower</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 21:55:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
